definitions.definition: ( uncountable , informal ) Any semi- solid or liquid substance; especially one that is sticky , gummy or slippery , unpleasant, and of vague or unknown composition, such as slime or semen .
examples: I stepped in some goo and had a terrible time getting the sticky stuff off my shoes.

main_definition: ( uncountable , informal ) Any semi- solid or liquid substance; especially one that is sticky , gummy or slippery , unpleasant, and of vague or unknown composition, such as slime or semen .

definitions.definition: A noise made by a baby trying to imitate speech.
examples: The infant's goos and gahs were endearing.

main_definition: A noise made by a baby trying to imitate speech.
